# Title: Activity from Infrequent Country
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-08-23
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when a Microsoft Cloud App Security reported when an activity occurs from a location that wasn't recently or never visited by any user in the organization.
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1573
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/cloud/m365/threat_management/microsoft365_activity_from_infrequent_country.yml

eventName="Activity from infrequent country" eventSource="SecurityComplianceCenter" status="success"